Go to the front of the microwave.
Open the microwave door. Put the board and the microwave in. Close the door. Turn on the microwave for five seconds. Open the microwave door. Take out the board with the mug.

Place the board on top of each other and the mug to the left near the wall.

Turn around to walk to the countertop to the right of the fridge.
Put the mug on top of the other mug on the countertop.
